+# UnusedConstructor
+
+Emitted when `--find-dead-code` is turned on and Psalm cannot find any uses of a given private constructor or function
+
+```php
+<?php
+
+class A {
+    private function __construct() {}
+
+    public static function createInstance() : void {}
+}
+A::createInstance();
+```
